      "description": [
        "{{sbc|Innate:}} '''Brand's''' [[Champion ability|abilities]] set his targets {{tip|DoT|ablaze}} for 4 seconds, dealing {{ft|{{as|3% of their '''maximum''' health}} over {{fd|3.25}} seconds|{{as|1% of their '''maximum''' health}} every {{fd|1.08{{recurring|3}}}} seconds}} as {{as|magic damage}}. Abilities used on an ''ablazed'' target are empowered and apply other [[stack]]s of ''Blaze'' while also refreshing the duration of the previous ones. A target can have up to 3 ''Blaze'' stacks at the same time. The damage per tick against monsters is increased by 20%, but capped at 80.",
        "Killing an enemy that is ''ablazed'' restores {{as|{{sti|mana|{{passive progression/deprecated version|7|20 to 40|1;3 to 18}} mana}}}}.",
        "After reaching 3 stacks on {{tip|monster|large monsters}} or enemy {{tip|champion|champions}}, an area is marked around the target which grants {{tip|sight}} in its radius and explodes after 2 seconds, consuming all the stacks. All enemies struck are dealt {{as|{{passive progression/deprecated version|9|key=%|12 to 16}}|health}}{{ft|{{as|(+ {{fd|1.5}}% per 100 AP)}}|{{as|(+ 1% per 66 AP)}}}} {{as|of their '''maximum''' health}} as {{as|magic damage}} and have a stack of ''Blaze'' applied to them. ''The explosion will still trigger if the target dies to the ability reaching 3 stacks or during the delay.''",
        "'''Brand''' cannot stack ''Blaze'' more than once on enemies who have exploded in the past 4 seconds."
      ],
      "leveling": [],
      "notes": "* ''Blaze'' is a debuff that persists through [[death]].\n* The explosion is not considered a tether effect and will not affect {{tip|untargetable}} targets, even if the explosion originated from them.\n* Each stack deals the damage individually and will always consider the time it was applied for deciding when the ticks will be applied, even when the duration refreshes.\n** At sub-optimal applied times, 2 stacks will deal a minimum of {{as|6% '''maximum''' health}} damage over 4 seconds, but will deal {{as|7% '''maximum''' health}} at optimal applied times.\n** Against small-medium units 3 stacks will deal a minimum of {{as|9% '''maximum''' health}} at sub-optimal times, but {{as|11% '''maximum''' health}} at optimal times. If these stacks are further {{tt|refreshed|By ablazing a target that's already at 3 stacks}} at optimal times they can deal up to {{as|12% '''maximum''' health}} over 4 seconds.\n* The burn is {{tip|persistent damage}} and the explosion is {{tip|area damage}}.",
      "skillkey": "I",
      "skillid": "i1",
      "effects": []
